Edgewater was initially listed on the 1950<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www2.census.gov/prod2/decennial/documents/37778831v2p2ch3.pdf |title=General Characteristics : Alabama : List of Tables |website=2.census.gov |access-date=June 15, 2016}}</ref> U.S. Census as an unincorporated community. It did not appear again until 2000 when it was designated a CDP (Census Designated Place).

